Version 1.0 — January 2026 Prepared by: Calum William O'Gorman, Founder & Director

1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY
Trip Tailors is a technology-enabled platform that empowers independent travel agents worldwide by providing them with professional branding, lead generation, AI-powered client tools, training, and a booking infrastructure — without requiring agents to surrender their independence, credentials, or insurance.

 Agents remain fully independent contractors with their own indemnity insurance, while Trip Tailors provides the tools, leads, and brand to accelerate their success.

Host agencies, which historically served as intermediaries providing accreditation, supplier contracts, and basic administrative support to independent travel agents, have become increasingly outdated in the modern travel industry. With the advent of advanced AI-poweredbooking platforms, traditional accreditation is no longer required to access competitive commissions, supplier inventories, or real-time reservation systems, rendering the core value proposition of host agencies obsolete. Independent agents today can achieve greater efficiency and profitability through specialized technology providers that deliver targeted leads, personalized training, and intelligent tools without the restricting rules and limited innovation typical of legacy host agencies. This shift empowers agents to operate with full autonomy and superior resources, eliminating the need for outdated affiliations that no longer align with the demands of a digital-first marketplace.
